OL,3,CSister of man missing in Spain says
OL,4,Cher 'heart is ripping'
OL,6,FThe sister of a man who has been
OL,7,Fmissing in south-eastern Spain for
OL,8,Fmore than a week has told UTV that her
OL,9,F'heart is ripping' as the search for
OL,10,Fhim goes on.
OL,12,FJohn Hardy hasn't been in contact with
OL,13,Ffriends or family since Saturday 14
OL,14,FDecember.
OL,16,FHe was due to return home to Northern
OL,17,FIreland on 18 December but wasn't on
OL,18,Fhis flight.
