OL,3,CSister of man missing in Spain says
OL,4,Cher 'heart is ripping'
OL,6,FMr Hardy, 37, had travelled to
OL,7,FAlicante where he was to drive to the
OL,8,Fpopular holiday resort town of
OL,9,FBenidorm to meet and stay over with a
OL,10,Ffriend.
OL,12,FHowever, his sister Courtney believes
OL,13,Fthat her older brother never made it
OL,14,Fto Benidorm.
OL,16,F"As the days go on, it's just not
OL,17,Fgood," she said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
