OL,3,CSister of man missing in Spain says
OL,4,Cher 'heart is ripping'
OL,6,F"Because as the days go on, you're
OL,7,Fthinking everything. Everything is
OL,8,Fgoing on in your head. You're worried
OL,9,Fsick, you're thinking of the worst and
OL,10,Fpeople are saying he's probably
OL,11,Fpartying. He's not partying."
OL,13,FMr Hardy from west Belfast, is a
OL,14,Ffather to two sons. His father went
OL,15,Fout to Spain over the last few days to
OL,16,Ftalk to police and to raise awareness
OL,17,Fabout his missing son.
OL,19,F"I know he's not going to be home for
OL,20,FChristmas," added Courtney.
