OL,3,CSister of man missing in Spain says
OL,4,Cher 'heart is ripping'
OL,6,F"He has two sons, and they need their
OL,7,Fdaddy."
OL,9,FA Go Fund Me page has also raised
OL,10,Fnearly #10,000 in a bid to allow as
OL,11,Fmany people as possible to join the
OL,12,Fsearch for their loved one in Spain.
OL,14,FHis family says all expenses will be
OL,15,Fcovered through any donations.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the Foreign and
OL,18,FCommonwealth Office said: "We are
OL,19,Fsupporting the family of a British man
OL,20,Freported missing in Spain and are in
OL,21,Fcontact with the local authorities."
